From: MC20018 <winme2001@outlook.com>
Date: Sun, 21 Jun 2026 14:37:58 +0800
Subject: [PATCH] Fand: reduce entity AI allocation hot paths

Add direct entity-section scans for item entity merging, area effect cloud application, and common AI target lookups.

Route nearest-target goals through a shared direct ServerEntityGetter helper so dense mob scenes avoid materializing candidate lists before TargetingConditions evaluation.

Replace several follow and anger propagation list/stream paths with direct loops while keeping vanilla selection rules and fallback behavior behind Fand performance flags.

